headline: Cadence Design Systems (NasdaqGS:CDNS) Price Rises 14% Over Last Quarter
summary: In May 2025, Cadence Design Systems (NasdaqGS:CDNS) launched the Millennium M2000 Supercomputer, delivering enhanced AI-accelerated simulations, alongside the Tensilica NeuroEdge 130 AI Co-Processor, optimizing neural processing. Despite these advancements, broader market trends like investor optimism over reduced tariffs between the U.S. and China may have provided a conducive environment for Cadence's stock price to rise 14% during the last quarter, aligning with the broader technology...
